    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时空之石》是一款半自动战斗的Rougelike角色扮演游戏。组建一支各司其职的小队，构筑独特技能流派，打造强力装备。作为一名指挥官，玩家需要制定合理的战斗策略，并即时操控队伍躲避危险，使战斗化险为夷，战胜强大的怪物与对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  欢迎大家加群交流</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  QQ群：191922791</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/b720832aab584ed58bc4cf3628487f01.poster.avif?t=1769285075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/b720832aab584ed58bc4cf3628487f01.webm?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/b720832aab584ed58bc4cf3628487f01.mp4?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择不一样的冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次出发世界的组成都会发生变化，你会遭遇不同的事件，挑战不同的BOSS，获取多种强大的装备，学习独特的技能。有些奖励同时也伴随着风险，甚至要付出惨痛的代价，每一次抉择都至关重要，当然运气也是实力的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/ff271857ab3cfac8829737958bcb0838.poster.avif?t=1769285075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/ff271857ab3cfac8829737958bcb0838.webm?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/ff271857ab3cfac8829737958bcb0838.mp4?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建不同的阵容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏没有固定的职业，通过在冒险中获取各种各样的技能，搭配多种随机词条的装备，组合出完全不同的阵容搭配，获取不一样的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/bea37a8e7406bbce8643e202b0f30f98.poster.avif?t=1769285075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/bea37a8e7406bbce8643e202b0f30f98.webm?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/bea37a8e7406bbce8643e202b0f30f98.mp4?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗方式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术安排：战斗开始前，你需要根据敌人和战斗的形式，巧妙的安排好战术，为不同英雄制定正确的技能施放策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动战斗：英雄们虽然听从于你，但他们的脑子都是一根筋，一旦战斗开始，他们会将你布置的策略进行到底。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即时指挥：在战斗中，玩家无法对英雄进行实时操控，但可以适时的使用指挥能力来调整队伍的站位，或是集火目标，在关键时刻可以化险为夷。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/8fed54ee392590b1d944b4e8ffd26e6d.poster.avif?t=1769285075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/8fed54ee392590b1d944b4e8ffd26e6d.webm?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/8fed54ee392590b1d944b4e8ffd26e6d.mp4?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时停指挥官：英雄乱打乱撞，指挥手忙脚乱，当战场无法控制的时候，可以启用时间停止进行紧急战略调整，做一个时停指挥官，再也不用担心英雄乱套。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/1c643ce7c16b48d0794310e0a24cce94.poster.avif?t=1769285075\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/1c643ce7c16b48d0794310e0a24cce94.webm?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262950/extras/1c643ce7c16b48d0794310e0a24cce94.mp4?t=1769285075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
